item.title: When Duty Calls
item.description: My first official post Alright. I realised that my first post wasn’t supposed to be online, so I had to remove it for good reasons. Anyhow, I’m still keen on getting my first official data science post up, so here we go! Mediacorp Channel 8 Prime Time To start off, I need to introduce some facts about myself. I not too recently got married, got my own house, and my own television.
